The files in this directory (`scanner.c` and `include/tree_sitter/{parser,array,alloc}.h`)
are vendored verbatim from tree-sitter/tree-sitter-python @ 0.25.0
(commit 293fdc02038ee2bf0e2e206711b69c90ac0d413f).

They are compiled into a small local C target (`CPythonScanner`) only to work around the
grammar's SwiftPM manifest, which never compiles `scanner.c` for a remote dependency (its
relative `fileExists("src/scanner.c")` check fails during manifest evaluation — see
tree-sitter/tree-sitter-python#330). Drop this target once that fix ships in a release.

Original license follows.

